quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,53,Proclaim O My servus exceeded limits nunquam despair de deus mercy! Pro DEUS forgives totus sins He est Forgiver Merciful
  39,54,Vos obey tuus Dominus submit Eum totally retribution overtakes vos; tunc vos non helped
  39,55,Subsequentis bene path ut pointed vos tuus Dominus retribution overtakes vos suddenly when vos minus expect it
  39,56,Lest anima dictus Quam sorry ego est disregarding deus commandments; ego est certainly 1 de mockers
  39,57,Dictus Habet DEUS guided me ego est cum the righteous
  39,58,Alias dictus when it vide retribution ego get alias chance ego work righteousness
  39,59,sic indeed (vos perfecit get satis chances My proofs advenit vos vos rejected them turned arrogant became disbeliever)
  39,60,Feria Resurrection vos vide faces de those qui lied DEUS covered cum misery. est Hell non rectus retribution pro arrogant unus
  39,61,DEUS testimentum save those maintained righteousness; He reward them. Non harm touch them nor testimentum they habet any grief
  39,62,DEUS est Creator TOTUS things He est in FODERATOR control TOTUS things
  39,63,To Eum belongs totus decisions caelum terra those disbelieve deus revelations est real losers